_:Nf0d3b5a431ae4f468e14a68cb1ad5204 <http://schema.org/description> "The East West Railway Company is a non-departmental public arm’s length body set up by the government to accelerate the East West Rail project – a new rail link between Cambridge and Oxford. EWRC is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Transport ." .
